    "created_at": "2016-03-09T08:28:50Z",
    "updated_at": "2016-03-09T08:28:57Z",
    "body": "Ahh you're definitely right—if there are other controls beneath (like the tabs) you really need to specify them separately... We can definitely make them different config settings, but I really wish we could keep the BrowserWindow config from becoming a mess! Maybe `titleBarHeight` is still an appropriate property name, we just won't change the positioning of the window controls?\n"
